        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 49. Valves of species of the informal group ‘Macroscapha tensa-opaca’. Macroscapha cactus sp. nov.: A, B, holotype adult male (SNB 0041, ZMH K-41483). Macroscapha falcis sp. nov.: C, D, paratype adult male (SNB 0472-DNA 179); G, H, subfossils (A-1); Q, subfossil (A-1), (ZMH K-41496). Macroscapha solecavai sp. nov.: E, F, paratype adult male (SNB 0560-DNA 267); J, K, paratype (A-1) female (SNB 0568-DNA 275, ZMH K-41499); I, paratype subfossil (A-?3, ZMH K-41498). Macroscapha opaca Maddocks, 1990: L, M (A-1) female (SNB 0506-DNA 213, ZMH K-42018). N, P, subfossil (A-2) (ZMH K-41495); O, subfossil (A-1) (ZMH K-40831). Macroscapha sp. nov. 1: R, subfossil A, (ZMH K-33305). A, C, E, left valve (LV) internal view; B, D, F, right valve (RV) internal view; G, J, L, N, RV external view; H, I, K, M, O, P, LV external view; Q, RLV dorsal view; R, RLV ventral view. Scale bar = 500 Mm. The arrows point towards the anterior of the animal." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4890174/files/figure.png" .

